{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1700-08_064", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Reponse de Mademoiselle de Scudery]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", août 1700 [tome 8], p. 64-67."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mademoiselle de Scudery répondit à cette galanterie par une autre de son esprit, qui est toujours le même. Il y avoit pour suscription."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "“Réponse à M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " de Vertron, Historiographe du Roy, &c. sur les Vers qu’il a faits au bas du Portrait qu’il m’a envoyé pour Bouquet.”"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vertron, vous me flatez d’une telle maniere,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Que j’en rougis de honte, au lieu d’en estre fiere."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour faire mon Portrait, sans perdre vostre temps,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Il faudroit me peindre à vingt ans."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Voila, genereux Vertron, ce que je puis répondre aux Vers qui sont au bas de l’ingenieux Portrait que vous m’avez donné, mais pour l’obligeante & agreable Prose, & les Vers qui l’accompagnent."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Vertron, ne trouvez pas étrange"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Si je n’accepte au plus qu’une unique loüange."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ay le cœur tendre & bon, sans nulle vanité,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui ne manque jamais à qui l’a merité."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Croyez donc, s’il vous plaist, sans nulle défiance,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Que vous pouvez compter sur ma reconnoissance,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": " Et qu’elle durera toujours,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " Jusques à la fin de mes jours."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Voila, Monsieur, ce qu’un grand rhume me permet de répondre à tant de belles choses, que vous me faites l’honneur de m’écrire. Je les montreray avec le Portrait, à des Personnes, dont les loüanges valent mieux que les miennes. Je suis, Monsieur, avec toute l’estime que vous meritez, vostre, &c."}]}]}